{"tid":665764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃安嗆蔡英文若能國機國造　「本帥就陪妳睡 ，絕不食言 」","createTime":"2018-05-15T08:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T09:17:20.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff84854d08eadee1c281c654c0d921b831be6d7","tid":665764,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:53:53.000Z","msg":"黃安嗆蔡英文若能國機國造　「本帥就陪妳睡」<br />\n<br />\n為提升國軍戰力，蔡英文政府於國防部前部長馮世寬任內啟動國機國造、國艦國造的國防自主重要計畫，對此，定居中國發展的藝人黃安嗆聲，「妳蔡英文能造出一架順豐快遞(中國速遞公司)的飛機，我本帥黃安就陪妳睡」。<br />\n<br />\n黃安在《微博》分享「我對台灣有話說」影片，提到他每次看蔡英文的《臉書》，都有一種想跳起來捶她的衝動，因為蔡英文說：「國機國造、國機國修，不只要自己的飛機自己修，還要打國際盃，邁向國際市場，修別人的飛機」，讓黃安怒批蔡英文又在騙了，酸說桃園機場的跑道坑坑洞洞，修了幾年都沒修好，連跑到都修不好怎麼修自己的飛機，嗆聲：「妳蔡英文能造出一架順豐快遞的飛機，我本帥黃安就陪妳睡，絕不食言」。<br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180515/1354277/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180515%2F1354277%2F&d=BRltTxiy%2FjBf63PtM8VK2DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3dac3520\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180515%2F1354277%2F&h=2a6e4224\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180515/1354277/</a>"},{"pid":"41bbb699b29435fc8fca73718e5c1cab43065ed5","tid":665764,"uid":653,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"英文：想呃床訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590496276137249c4122b1ab53ebd849eb472e75","tid":665764,"uid":77196,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:57:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母搵塊鏡照下自己個樣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0d43d7093e8bf6d5f56e516fdd3dc6806bd38c","tid":665764,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:00:11.000Z","msg":"黄安 邊位來+？"},{"pi